# =============================================================================
# autoconf-archive - GNU Autoconf Macro Archive
# =============================================================================
# Collection of freely reusable Autoconf macros including AX_PTHREAD,
# AX_CHECK_COMPILE_FLAG, AX_CXX_COMPILE_STDCXX, and many others.

